Package net.okocraft.box.api.taskfactory

Interface TaskFactory

@Deprecated(since="5.5.0", forRemoval=true) @ScheduledForRemoval(inVersion="6.0.0") public interface TaskFactory
Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
use BoxScheduler
An interface to create CompletableFutures.

    • run

      @NotNull @NotNull CompletableFuture<Void> run(@NotNull @NotNull Runnable task)
      Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
      Creates a CompletableFuture to run the task on the main thread.

      In Folia, the Runnable will be executed on Bukkit.getGlobalRegionScheduler().

      Parameters:
      task - the task to run
      Returns:
      the new CompletableFuture

    • runEntityTask

      @NotNull <E extends Entity> @NotNull CompletableFuture<Void> runEntityTask(@NotNull E target, @NotNull @NotNull Consumer<E> task)
      Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
      Creates a CompletableFuture to run the task on the main thread or entity's thread.

      This task will be executed on the next tick.

      Type Parameters:
      E - the entity type
      Parameters:
      target - the entity for which a task is performed
      task - the task
      Returns:
      the CompletableFuture
      Since:
      5.3.1
